  "SUBTITLE_SANFRAN_SFA_ADL_DOTHESESONSOFBITCHES": "^2Admiral Kelly: ^7这些狗娘养的以为能干掉第七舰队？他们会大吃一惊的。",
  "SUBTITLE_SANFRAN_SFA_ADL_SENTINELONEWHATTHEHELL": "^2Admiral Kelly: ^7哨兵一号，上面到底怎么回事？",
  "SUBTITLE_SANFRAN_SFA_ADL_SERGEANTCORMACKINEEDA": "^2Admiral Kelly: ^7科马克军士，我需要一个该死的形势报告。",
  "SUBTITLE_SANFRAN_SFA_ADL_SONOFABITCHMAN": "^2Admiral Kelly: ^7操他妈的，进入战斗岗位。",
  "SUBTITLE_SANFRAN_SFA_ADL_WHATTHEHELL": "^2Admiral Kelly: ^7搞什么？",
  "SUBTITLE_SANFRAN_SFA_ADS_COPYSENTINELZEROONE": "^2Admiral Davis: ^7收到，哨兵零一。一切看起来如常。我们能确认这情报可靠吗，少校？",
  "SUBTITLE_SANFRAN_SFA_ADS_COPYTHAT": "^2Kingpin: ^7收到。正在拦截。",
  "SUBTITLE_SANFRAN_SFA_ADS_SENTINELZEROONEINEEDASITREP": "^2Kingpin: ^7哨兵零一，我需要形势报告。",
  "SUBTITLE_SANFRAN_SFA_ADS_SENTINELZEROONETHECARRIERISALMOST": "^2Kingpin: ^7哨兵零一，航母几乎已离开大桥。",
  "SUBTITLE_SANFRAN_SFA_ADS_SENTINELZEROONETHISISADMIRALDAVIS": "^2Kingpin: ^7哨兵零一，我是金平。你的情况如何？",
  "SUBTITLE_SANFRAN_SFA_ADS_THECARRIERISREPORTINGA": "^2Admiral Davis: ^7航母报告出现大规模伤亡！",
  "SUBTITLE_SANFRAN_SFA_ADS_UNDERSTOODWEREMANNINGBATTLESTATIONS": "^2Kingpin: ^7收到。我们正在进入战斗岗位。",
  "SUBTITLE_SANFRAN_SFA_ALX_ROGERTHAT": "^2Alexi: ^7收到。",
  "SUBTITLE_SANFRAN_SFA_ALX_SOMETHINGSGOINGONWITHTHOSE": "^2Alexi: ^7那些货船不对劲！",
  "SUBTITLE_SANFRAN_SFA_ALX_WEVEGOTTWOCARGOSHIPS": "^2Alexi: ^7有两艘货船从西边驶来。MASINT已放行。",
  "SUBTITLE_SANFRAN_SFA_COP_BLOODYHELL": "^2Cop: ^2真他妈见鬼",
  "SUBTITLE_SANFRAN_SFA_COP_ICANTBELIEVEIT": "^2Cop: ^7我简直不敢相信……",
  "SUBTITLE_SANFRAN_SFA_COP_THEYJUSTFELLRIGHTIN": "^2Cop: ^7他们就那么掉进去了……",
  "SUBTITLE_SANFRAN_SFA_COP_THEYREALLDEAD": "^2Cop: ^7他们都死了……",
  "SUBTITLE_SANFRAN_SFA_COP_THISISNTPOSSIBLE": "^2Cop: ^7这不可能……",
  "SUBTITLE_SANFRAN_SFA_CRK_ADMIRALCLEARYOURMENOFF": "^2Cormack: ^7上将，让你的人离开甲板！",
  "SUBTITLE_SANFRAN_SFA_CRK_ADMIRALCOMEIN": "^2Cormack: ^7上将，收到请回答！",
  "SUBTITLE_SANFRAN_SFA_CRK_ADMIRALDAVISTHISISSENTINELZEROONE": "^2Cormack: ^7戴维斯上将，这里是哨兵零一。我们已在舰队周围建立了防线，完毕。",
  "SUBTITLE_SANFRAN_SFA_CRK_ADMIRALKELLYTHEVANIS": "^2Cormack: ^7凯利上将，厢型车已控制，阿特拉斯的部队已经……搞什么？",
  "SUBTITLE_SANFRAN_SFA_CRK_ADMIRALWEAREENGAGEDWITH": "^2Cormack: ^7金平，我们正在大桥上与大量阿特拉斯部队交战。我们需要封锁任何驶入的船只。",
  "SUBTITLE_SANFRAN_SFA_CRK_ADMIRALWEHAVEENEMYTARGETS": "^2Cormack: ^7上将，大桥上有敌方目标。所有单位红色警戒。",
  "SUBTITLE_SANFRAN_SFA_CRK_ADMIRALWEREINTHEMIX": "^2Cormack: ^7上将，我们正在大桥上与大量阿特拉斯部队混战。",
  "SUBTITLE_SANFRAN_SFA_CRK_ADMIRALYOUVEGOT30PLUS": "^2Cormack: ^7上将，有30多架FAB无人机正朝你们飞来。",
  "SUBTITLE_SANFRAN_SFA_CRK_ALLUNITSWEHAVEMULTIPLE": "^2Cormack: ^7所有单位，多辆阿特拉斯车辆正在向大桥集结！我需要立即建立对舰队的全向防御！",
  "SUBTITLE_SANFRAN_SFA_CRK_ARCLIGHT": "^2Cormack: ^7弧光。",
  "SUBTITLE_SANFRAN_SFA_CRK_ATLASVEHICLESAREDEPLOYINGSOLDIERS": "^2Cormack: ^7阿特拉斯的车辆正在部署士兵！他们在靠近你的位置！",
  "SUBTITLE_SANFRAN_SFA_CRK_BURKE": "^2Cormack: ^7伯克！",
  "SUBTITLE_SANFRAN_SFA_CRK_BURKETHEVANISLAME": "^2Cormack: ^7伯克，厢型车跑不动了。我们把他们困住了，在桥的正中央。",
  "SUBTITLE_SANFRAN_SFA_CRK_GETBACKEVERYONEGETBACK": "^2Cormack: ^7后退！所有人都后退！",
  "SUBTITLE_SANFRAN_SFA_CRK_GIDEONMITCHELLREPORTIN": "^2Cormack: ^7吉迪恩，汇报情况。",
  "SUBTITLE_SANFRAN_SFA_CRK_GIDEONWEVEGOTTHEVAN": "^2Cormack: ^7吉迪恩，我们把厢型车困住了，在桥的正中央。",
  "SUBTITLE_SANFRAN_SFA_CRK_GIDEONYOUHAVEEXECUTEAUTHORITY": "^2Cormack: ^7你已获授权摧毁那辆厢型车。",
  "SUBTITLE_SANFRAN_SFA_CRK_INEEDAROADBLOCKMIDSPAN": "^2Cormack: ^7我需要路障，桥中央！",
  "SUBTITLE_SANFRAN_SFA_CRK_KEEPEMONICEUNTIL": "^2Cormack: ^7困住他们，等舰队离开大桥。",
  "SUBTITLE_SANFRAN_SFA_CRK_KINGPINWEHAVEENEMYTARGETS": "^2Cormack: ^7金平，大桥上有敌方目标。所有单位红色警戒。",
  "SUBTITLE_SANFRAN_SFA_CRK_NEGATIVETHEVANSTHEPRIORITY": "^2Cormack: ^7不行，厢型车是首要目标！",
  "SUBTITLE_SANFRAN_SFA_CRK_NEGITIVEWECANNOTGO": "^2Cormack: ^7不行，我们不能使用动能武器，平民太多了。",
  "SUBTITLE_SANFRAN_SFA_CRK_PUTTHOSEBIRDSONTHE": "^2Cormack: ^7让那些飞机立刻落地！别让他们跑了！",
  "SUBTITLE_SANFRAN_SFA_CRK_SFPDISONTHESCENE": "^2Cormack: ^7旧金山警察局到场了！",
  "SUBTITLE_SANFRAN_SFA_CRK_TAKETHEMOUT": "^2Cormack: ^7干掉他们！干掉他们！",
  "SUBTITLE_SANFRAN_SFA_CRK_THANKS": "^2Cormack: ^7谢谢。",
