  "SUBTITLE_SANFRAN_SFA_CRK_THERECOULDBEANYTHINGINSIDE": "^2Cormack: ^7那辆厢型车里面可能有任何东西。追踪但不要交火。",
  "SUBTITLE_SANFRAN_SFA_CRK_WEARESENDINGMENTO": "^2Cormack: ^7我们正在派人支援，上将。",
